{"word":"δημιουργέω","slug":"δημιουργέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>δημιουργέω</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:δημιουργός'><el>δημιουργός</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to practise a trade, do work</i>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a> rei, <i>to work at, fabricate</i>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>to be one of the</i> <el>δημιουργοί</el> (II), <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}